<br>
my utter frustration this evening came from two things.  one, casting a 400 mana heal, my absolute best heal in my book, and seeing my tanks hp, a freakin ranger no less, go up only 4/5th of  a bubble.  and two, spending 1200 mana to heal a melee 2 1/2 bubs, while at the same time seeing the cleric spend 400 to heal the other melee 4 1/2 bubs.<br>
